(190,'Yoshihiro Hojima ','81-6-6115-6800','hojima@imc-osa.co.jp','M/S Sim  Trading Co., Ltd.\r\nAttn : Purchasing Manager\r\n\r\nDear Sir and Madam\r\n\r\nGood morning.\r\n\r\nFirst of all, please let us allow to introduce ourselves as we are one of leading Trading Company for various kinds of component parts for kitchen equipment.\r\nWe have been exporting our products to South East Asia market included Vietnam.\r\n\r\nBut recently we have been exporting various kinds of Japanese Kitchenware & Tableware and etc. to above-mentioned markets.\r\nTaking this opportunity, we would like to establish long and reliable business relation with your Esteemed company for mutual benefit.\r\n\r\nIn this case, one of our customer introduced your company as one of the leading importer and distributor \r\nof Japanese foods.\r\n\r\nThen we introduce genuine Japanese Matcha Powder to you.\r\nWe know that you have a good and strong channel in this field.\r\nYou can sell Matcha Powder ( Matcha Leaf and etc. ) to Supermarket, Convenience Store, Confection manufacturer, Restaurant.\r\nThese are only a part what we can supply and we can supply cheaper one(s) to you.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in our dealing items, of course we hope so, please contact us without hesitate.\r\nWe will send more details to you.\r\n\r\nWe are sure that we can supply all of the items that you need with special condition.\r\nWe always meet all customer needs in the fastest way.\r\n\r\nYour kind cooperation is highly appreciated.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nY. Hojima ( Mr. )\r\n***********************************************\r\nIMC OVERSEAS CORPORATION\r\n\r\n1-21-9, HARIMA-CHO, ABENO-KU, OSAKA, 545-0022, JAPAN\r\nTel : 81-6-6115-6800\r\nFax : 81-6-6622-6865\r\nE-Mail : hojima@imc-osa.co.jp\r\nURL : www.imc-osa.co.jp\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),
