(199,'Spirits Wholesaler Akitaya From Nagoya','07035388798','lin.ruikai@fbmg.co.jp','To Whom It May Concern\r\n \r\nGreeting from Japan and we hope you all well.\r\nThis is Rick from Akitaya Co Ltd（秋田屋） from Nagoya, Japan. We are the wholesaler of Japanese Liquors which established at 1855（安政二年）. \r\nRepresent as our CEO Mr. Asano who very interest in expanding our new business chance in Vietnam and whole ASEAN countries, he orders me to have contact with you.\r\nhttp://www.akita-ya.com/\r\n \r\nPlease kindly find the PDF attached for our company profile.\r\n \r\nCompare to those mega distributors in Japan, our strength is the relationship that we keep with the craft-men all around Japan. As our consideration, the circumstance of coronavirus in around the world has led a new boom which the people would drink at home and seek for the high-quality liquors in delicate works and appropriate price. Japanese Liquors which famous in their verities and multifarious way of drinking might be a good choice for the trend.\r\n \r\nHere might be a good chance for accumulating our Japanese Liquors fans in this period because we are not only offering only the liquors but also we can help to arrange a trip for those people who would interest in our cellars in Japan.\r\n \r\nIf you are interested in our company, please feel free to contact us and our CEO would like to have a meeting online with you to discuss how we can expand the business in your area. \r\n \r\nHere is our showroom located in Nagoya-Shi, we are always welcome you visit to our showroom to know more about our history.\r\nhttp://www.akita-ya.com/kura\r\n \r\nThe Rakuten Shop we are running for ToC selling,\r\nhttps://www.rakuten.ne.jp/gold/kurastyle/\r\n \r\nThe Facebook Page we running for targeting the female customers in Japan. We think that might be a good way for selling our liquors in Vietnam.\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/ochocogirl.pc/\r\nBest Regards,\r\n \r\nRick\r\nAKITAYA \r\n \r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),
(200,'Thi Trang','0327074151','jasmine.trang@tmforwarding.com','Xin chào anh/chị\r\nEm tên là Thi Trang, nhân viên kinh doanh của công ty T&M Forwarding.\r\nNhư anh chị đã biết, hiện nay nhu cầu sử dụng và trao đổi hàng hóa ngày càng phát triển, hoạt động về Logistics chiếm phần lớn trong chi phí doanh nghiệp. \r\nVới bề dày hơn 25 năm hoạt động trong ngành logistics, T&M Forwarding luôn tự tin cung cấp những dịch vụ logistics hiệu quả nhất với giá tốt. T&M Forwarding sẽ là lựa chọn tốt nhất để doanh nghiệp tin tưởng và sử dụng dịch vụ nhằm góp phần giảm tối đa chi phí, tăng lợi nhuận cho doanh nghiệp.\r\n•	Vận chuyển đường biển/ hàng không ( FCL,LCL,..) từ các ga, cảng, sân bay trong và ngoài nước\r\n•	Vận chuyển hàng thương mại điện tử ( Amazon, Alibaba, Shopify,….)\r\n•	Vận chuyển hàng công trình hàng dự án (hàng siêu trường, siêu trọng)\r\n•	Vận chuyển phát nhanh\r\n•	Khai thuê hải quan\r\n•	Dịch vụ kho bãi(lưu kho, đóng gói, dán nhãn, quản lý hàng hóa…)\r\n•	Quản trị logistics (ứng dụng cargowise one)\r\nEm rất mong sẽ được hợp tác với anh/ chị trong thời gian sắp tới. Xin cảm ơn.\r\nTrân trọng\r\n \r\nMs.Jasmine Trang\r\nSales Executive\r\n \r\nT&M Forwarding Ltd.\r\nWeb site: www.tmforwarding.com\r\nEmail: jasmine.trang@tmforwarding.com \r\nMobile: +84 327 074 151\r\nWhatapps: +84 327 074 151\r\nSkype: Jasmine. Trang\r\n \r\nT&M Forwarding \r\nCelebrating 25 years in global logistics\r\n1996 – 2021\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),
(201,'Yamamoto Noriten','07035388798','t-yamamoto@yamamoto-noriten.co.jp','To Whom It May Concern\r\n\r\nGreeting from Japan and we hope you all well.\r\nThis is YAMAMOTONORITEN Co Ltd（山本海苔店） from Tokyo, Japan. \r\nWe are the wholesaler and maker of Nori seaweed which established at 1849. \r\n\r\nAnd the largest wholesaler in Japan.\r\nRepresent as our CEO Mr. Yamamoto who very interest in expanding our new business chance in Poland, he orders me to have contact with you.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.yamamoto-noriten.co.jp/english/\r\nPlease kindly find the PDF attached for our company profile.\r\n\r\nCompare to those other makers in Japan, our strength is the we are not only make the premium nori seaweed which used by the Royal Family in Japan, but we also have the wide-price range of Nori seaweed . \r\nAs our consideration, the circumstance of coronavirus in around the world has led a new boom which the people would drink and eat more at home,\r\nand seek for the high-quality food in delicate works and appropriate price. \r\n\r\nIf you are interested in our company, please feel free to contact us and our CEO would like to have a meeting online with you to discuss how we can expand the business in your area. \r\n\r\nBest Regards,\r\nYamamoto\r\n\r\n\r\n',NULL,NULL,NULL),
