(203,'YAMAMOTO KAMABOKOTEN LTD','09093069373','morigaku4711@ybb.ne.jp','Dear Sirs\r\n\r\nYou will be highly appreciated if you can transfer this mail to your purchasing department. Thanks in advance.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDear Sirs\r\nFrom: Yamamoto Kamaboko Ltd. Japan\r\n \r\n \r\nYour name was given by JETRO(Japan External Trade Organization) whom you registered as interested buyer of Japanese goods to.\r\n \r\nWe also registered on Salad-Plate Web-Site as Japanese foods supplier, which is operated by JETRO, as matching site for Japanese foods suppliers and overseas buyers\r\n \r\n https:/www.saladplate.com/\r\n \r\nWe would like to introduce ourselves as Producer of Fish Cake (KAMABOKO in Japanese language) located in MUROTO, Kochi Pref.in Japan, where quite famous as big fishing port.\r\n \r\nWe are eager to expand the market to overseas where many people who are interested in Japanese foods and/or many Japanese are living.\r\n \r\nWe are proud of the excellent quality because of using high grade raw materials and  handmade.\r\n \r\nBrief of our products is as under.\r\n \r\n①    Retort products that can be stored at room temperature of which expiration is basically 90 days or 180 days depending on the products.\r\n\r\n②    Quick freezing products of which expiration is 1 year subject to be kept strictly under at -18℃ after production date and 7 days after defrost.\r\n\r\n③    Our epoch-making freezing technology is without using freezing agent in order to make texture supple even after defrost. \r\n\r\n \r\n (what kind of information you can get)\r\n\r\n    Products Name with photo of the products\r\n\r\n　　Features\r\n\r\n    Retail prices in Japan under exchange rate of Japanese yen105=1US$\r\n\r\n　　Raw materials\r\n\r\n    Packaging\r\n\r\n    Allergies information\r\n\r\n　　HALAL (Authenticated by Japan Halal Business Association)\r\n\r\n    The other specifications\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\nYou will be highly appreciated if you can check with Salad-Plate Web Site as mentioned above to know more details as above.\r\n \r\n(Wright as YAMAMOTO in Search column of 1st page of Salad Plate web site so that you can find the YAMAMOTO KAMABOKO’s page.\r\n \r\nOur Home-Page is as below but unfortunately the contents is only in Japanese but we wish you may be able to get some image about us and our products.\r\n \r\nhttp://muroto-kamabokoya.jp/\r\n \r\n\r\nWish you to be interested in our products and please do not hesitate to contact us through Salad-Plate Inquiry or directly mail to morigaku4711@ybb.ne.jp who is an adviser of YAMAMOTO KAMABOKO LTD\r\n \r\n \r\nBest regards\r\n \r\n           Gakuso Mori,　An adviser\r\n           On behalf of\r\nMr. Yamamoto, The President of Yamamoto Kamaboko Ltd',NULL,NULL,NULL),
