(206,'Akinobu Yumiba','0992689711','info@yumiba.co.jp','Dear Purchase manager,\r\n\r\nWe hope you are doing well.\r\n\r\nPlease let us introduce ourselves briefly.\r\nSince the establishment in 1981, we have been exporting the Japanese food such as Wagyu and Hamachi, Japanese Tea, \r\nConfectionary to USA and Hong Kong, etc.\r\nAlso, we have started to export Wagyu to Canada last year.\r\n\r\nKagoshima, Our company located, is surrounded by mild climate and rich nature, the number of Japanese Black Wagyu and Pig, Chicken are the largest in Japan. \r\nSo, Kagoshima is called “The Livestock Kingdom”.\r\nAs for Japanese Black Wagyu, Kagoshima accounts for about 20% of the nation\'s breeding head.\r\nAlso, it won first place in the latest competition “Wagyu Olympic” and the demand has been soaring in Japan.\r\nThe soft quality and good balance of marbling make for a rich flavor and melt-like texture by breeding carefully according to each individual.\r\n\r\nWe can supply suitable products according to customers order (rank, BMS).\r\nIf you are interested in our product, please kindly tell us your intention for a quotation.\r\n1)	Part & Specification \r\n2)	Quantity/Shipment\r\n\r\nLooking forward to do business with you for a long term.\r\n\r\nYour sincerely,\r\nAkinobu Yumiba\r\nYumiba Trading Co., Ltd.\r\n8-20 Oroshihonmachi,\r\nKagoshima City, Kagoshima 891-0123, Japan\r\nTEL +81-99-268-9711\r\nFAX +81-99-268-1353',NULL,NULL,NULL),
