(241,'Bregas Insan Kharisma','08071913541','bregas.kharisma@fbmg.co.jp','Dear Sim Ba Trading,\r\nTo whom it might concern,\r\n\r\nGreetings from Japan, we hope you are well.\r\n\r\nNice to e-meet you, my name is Bregas, from Family Business Management Co. Ltd., (https://fbmg.co.jp/lp_s/) We are a consulting firm specializing in providing services to well-established companies in Japan. We have formed alliances with mega-financial institutions in Japan, and we are always getting good leads. Our clients are predominantly Japanese \"family businesses\", which has been in business for as long as 50 to 400 years from a wide range of industries.\r\n\r\nI am now representing the CEO of YAMAMOTONORITEN Co Ltd（山本海苔店）Mr. Yamamoto who is very interested in expanding our new business chance in Vietnam. We would like to do a fruitful business contact with Sim Ba Trading.\r\n\r\nYAMAMOTONORITEN have been in the nori making business for more than 150 years since 1849 in Tokyo, the contribution includes inventing the flavored nori, and standardizing the size and shape of nori depending on its use. the long relationship with the nori farmers and experience in the business for long has sharpen their craftiness on creating the best and affordable nori. YAMAMOTONORITEN is proudly serving various kind of customers including the Japanese Imperial House.\r\n\r\nYAMAMOTONORITEN’s unique proposition to the market is, offering healthy nori snack present for family and friends. The nori chips produced are both tasty and give new taste experience which surely add value proposition for the customers.\r\nWe have collaborated with famous iconic Japanese character such as Hello Kitty, and Doraemon, as well with international events such as the Tokyo 2020 Olympics to create a special themed package (below).\r\n     \r\n\r\nOn top of that, YAMAMOTONORITEN also produces seaweed products for wholesale and kitchen use which normally seek for best quality but affordable price. In this lineup there are nori for seasoning, onigiri, sushi, and topping use. There is also option to produce OEM brand with you to promote your Private Brand with high quality and healthy Nori Seaweed, in this example, Tokyo Disneyland is one of the customers. \r\n\r\nBelow are some links for your reference:\r\nEnglish website : https://www.yamamoto-noriten.co.jp/english/\r\nProduct Lineup (Japanese retail price) : https://www.yamamotonori-shop.jp/c/all\r\nYAMAMOTONORITEN product in space (Japanese) :https://astro-mission.jaxa.jp/noguchi/\r\n\r\nWe are looking forward to work together with Sim Ba Trading.\r\nBest Regards,\r\n\r\nBregas',NULL,NULL,NULL),
