(247,'Sae Tsubuku','（+81）270508221','tsubuku@milkmarket-japan.com','Hello, I\'m Sae Tsubuku and I work at Milk Market Japan (MMJ).\r\nMMJ is the distributor of raw milk in Japan.\r\nI saw your website and I am mailing.\r\n\r\nToday, I want to introduce our new product \"Hokkaido Freeze Fried Milk\".\r\nIt\'s made from 100% milk from Hokkaido, and freeze-drying keeps the milk\'s taste and nutritional value.\r\n\r\n“Freeze Dried Milk” is powdered and has better taste and solubility than whole milk powder.\r\nFurther, it can be stored at room temperature and has a shelf life of 365 days.\r\nTherefore, logistics and storage costs can be significantly reduced.\r\n\r\nIt has a wide variety of uses, such as dissolving in hot water for drinking, making coffee, making sweets, and so on.\r\nYou can enjoy the taste of Hokkaido milk more easily.\r\nSamples can be ordered at any time.\r\n\r\nYou can find details of the product from our website.\r\nhttps://milkmarket-japan.com/freeze-dried-milk\r\n\r\nThank you very much for your time in reading this message.',NULL,NULL,NULL),
