df/3_4-To-trinh_thu-lao-HDQT-BKS.pdf\">3.4 To trinh_thu lao HDQT &ndash; BKS</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n','','','','','nghi-quyet-dai-hoi-dong-co-dong-cong-ty-co-phan-pymepharco','2022-04-26 20:36:33','/assets/images/placeholder.png',10,NULL,NULL,NULL),
